{
  "texts": [
    "On the Ph.D. level, ChatGPT provided decent answers but with a tendency to review current literature.",
    "These reviews can, however, miss critical reflections and are typically not exhaustive.",
    "We saw limited evidence of ChatGPT coming up with new research ideas or surprising syntheses of current literature.",
    "The use of ChatGPT has strong ethical implications.",
    "In our study, we observe that ChatGPT has some initial built-in safeguards to prevent unethical use."
  ]
}